Always set backoffLimit to avoid infinite retries on failure.
 â€¢ Use successfulJobsHistoryLimit and failedJobsHistoryLimit to manage job logs and cleanup.
 â€¢ Jobs do not automatically clean up pods or persistent storage unless you tell them to.
 â€¢ For CronJobs, consider time zones and concurrency policy (e.g., allow, forbid, replace).

