Need to run a daily backup of your PostgreSQL database at midnight?

âœ… Define a CronJob with schedule 0 0 * * *
âœ… Use a pod that connects to the DB and dumps data to cloud storage
âœ… Let Kubernetes handle the scheduling, retries, and logs

No external scheduler needed. Fully automated and native to the cluster.

